Text.Text: Death to Kuldahar and all who defy the will of the Cold Goddess!
In Auril's name, from winter's veil, my claw tears through the frozen air...  Neither your might, nor earthly means, will save you from your death's despair.

From the Sea of Moving Ice to the High Forest, from the highest peak in the Spine of the World Mountains, to the deepest, most volcanic bowels of the earth, the Legion of the Chimera will purge this land of those enemies who sought to deny the sovereignty of our nation!
